name: NY AG James

tweet: Monarch's scheme involved:  1⃣ Coaxing students into signing leases for housing  2⃣ Denying students access to that very housing  3⃣ Demanding students pay thousands of dollars in rent for housing they were denied  4⃣ Referring students to debt collectors for not paying this rent

name: NY AG James
tweet: Monarch 716, a student housing complex, preyed on students at @buffalostate through an illegal housing scheme, and my office is making them pay.  We're canceling over $200,000 in illegal housing debt and recouping tens of thousands for students who were deceived and threatened.
